- Use standalone components exclusively.
- Set `ChangeDetectionStrategy.OnPush` on every component.
- Prefer `signals` and `computed` for local state.
- Keep templates declarative and minimal; avoid complex logic.
- Extract complex logic into services or helpers.
- Avoid RxJS unless a stream is required; use signals where practical.
- Use semantic HTML and native controls first.
- Keep components single-responsibility and small.
- Use `inject()` for services when possible.
- Follow layered architecture: UI → services → adapters.